STATE
v.
SMITH 2018-1831 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 6, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion to supplement record. Motion granted. Clerk of the Hamilton County Court of Appeals ordered to supplement the record with the November 16, 2018 judgment entry for 1st Dist. Hamilton No. C-170335 within ten days.
